(30, 1, '2015-05-23 10:21:45', '2015-05-23 10:21:45', '	<div class="package content">\r\n	<div class="clearfix">\r\n		<div class="column">\r\n			<h2>BASIC</h2>\r\n			<p>Creative brief\r\nScript\r\nStoryboard\r\nVisuals (stock)\r\n2D Animation\r\nVoice over (EN)\r\nMusic (stock)\r\nSound FX\r\nOne Correction Round</p><br/><br/><br/><br/>\r\n	<p>For companies, mostly start-ups, looking for cost-effective yet high quality explainer videos to market their product or service.  </p>\r\n		</div>\r\n\r\n		<div class="column">\r\n			<h2>STANDARD</h2>\r\n			<p>Creative brief\r\nScript\r\nStoryboard\r\nVisuals (personalised)\r\n2D Animation\r\n2D Characters\r\n3D Animations (simple)\r\nVoice over (EN)\r\nMusic (stock)\r\nSound FX\r\nTwo Correction Rounds</p><br/>\r\n	<p>For companies with a higher but strict budget. The Package is inclusive of unique character design and generally consists of more animation.  </p>\r\n		</div>\r\n\r\n		<div class="column">\r\n			<h2>PRO</h2>\r\n			<p>Creative brief\r\nScript\r\nStoryboard\r\nVisuals (personalised)\r\n2D Animation\r\n2D Characters\r\n3D Animation (advanced)\r\nVoice over (EN)\r\nMusic (personalised)\r\nSound FX\r\nThree Correction Rounds\r\nLogo animation</p><br/><br/>\r\n	<p>For companies looking for a premium  2D animation combined with motion graphics and 3D \r\nelements.</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class="column">\r\n			<h2>CUSTOM</h2><br/>\r\n	<p>Looking for a TV commercial? Or 3d Animation? Specific duration?\r\n\r\nwe’ll help you customize the best video package based on all your requirements.</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n\r\n		<center>\r\n		<p>We’d love to</p>\r\n		<a class="button" href="http://localhost/storywise/get-a-quote/">HELP</a></center>\r\n		<br/><br/><br/><br/>\r\n	</div>', 'OUR PACKAGES', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'packages', '', '', '2015-05-30 17:24:32', '2015-05-30 17:24:32', '', 0, 'http://localhost/storywise/?page_id=30', 0, 'page', '', 0),
